    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 2,
    "last_activity_date" : 1525617518,
    "last_edit_date" : 1525617518,
    "creation_date" : 1471410846,
    "answer_id" : 38988563,
    "question_id" : 3930210,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Simple way is just concatenate <code>\"\"</code> with integer:</p>\n\n<pre><code>int i = 100;\n\nString s = \"\" + i;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>now <code>s</code> will have <code>100</code> as string value.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 6961607,
      "reputation" : 2292,
      "user_id" : 5340833,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/cf0a61973f4c160ee00cbcd20cd1ae2c?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "Py-Coder",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/5340833/py-coder"
